<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Configurar 2FA</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-900 min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center">
  <div class="bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg max-w-md w-full">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Configurar Autenticación en Dos Pasos</h1>
    
    <div class="mb-6 text-center">
      <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">Escanea este código QR con Google Authenticator:</p>
      <div class="flex justify-center mb-6">
        <img src="<%= qrCodeDataURL %>" alt="Código QR 2FA" class="w-48 h-48 border-4 border-white rounded-lg">
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Después de escanear, ingresa el código de 6 dígitos que aparece en la app</p>
    </div>

    <form action="/2fa/setup" method="POST" class="space-y-4">
      <div>
        <label for="token" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-300">Código de verificación</label>
        <input type="text" id="token" name="token" required 
               class="mt-1 block w-full px-3 py-2 bg-gray-700 border border-gray-600 rounded-md shadow-sm text-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:border-indigo-500"
               placeholder="000000" pattern="\d{6}" title="Ingresa los 6 dígitos">
      </div>

      <button type="submit" class="w-full flex justify-center py-2 px-4 border border-transparent rounded-md shadow-sm text-sm font-medium text-white bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-indigo-500">
        Verificar y Activar
      </button>
    </form>
  </div>
</body>
</html>